OL,3,C'He inspires all of us': Man with
OL,4,Cunique genetic variation gets 'dream
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FA man who has a rare genetic variation
OL,8,Fis "thriving" in his "dream job"
OL,9,Fthanks to a charity for disabled
OL,10,Fchildren.
OL,12,FHarry Clayton is the only person known
OL,13,Fto have his chromosome anomaly, which
OL,14,Fwas found in a blood test when he was
OL,15,Fyoung. He has limited communication
OL,16,Fdue to his unclear speech and is
OL,17,Funable to read or write.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
