PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773256282
OL,3,C'He inspires all of us': Man with
OL,4,Cunique genetic variation gets 'dream
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FCheshire-based charity the Seashell
OL,8,FTrust provides education and care for
OL,9,Fthose with the most complex
OL,10,Fdisabilities.
OL,12,FThe charity runs an Employability
OL,13,FPathway for student with additional
OL,14,Fneeds, and helped Harry gain paid
OL,15,Femployment at the Light cinema in
OL,16,FStockport.
OL,18,FHe also works as part of the
OL,19,Fmaintenance team at Seashell, having
OL,20,Fpreviously completed an internship at
OL,21,FRoyal College Manchester.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
