OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773256282
OL,3,C'He inspires all of us': Man with
OL,4,Cunique genetic variation gets 'dream
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FHarry's "best mate" Jim, who works on
OL,8,Fthe maintenance team alongside him and
OL,9,Fsaid the 23-year-old has "come on
OL,10,Fleaps and bounds" said: "He just
OL,11,Fcracks on with anything you give him.
OL,12,FHe'll turn his hand to anything you
OL,13,Fask him to do."
OL,15,F"It's because of that individuality
OL,16,Fand that independence. It's great to
OL,17,Fsee these guys come on."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
