PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773256282
OL,3,C'He inspires all of us': Man with
OL,4,Cunique genetic variation gets 'dream
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FSeashell's Employability Pathway sees
OL,8,F25% of students go into paid work-
OL,9,F four times the national average for
OL,10,Fstudents with additional needs gaining
OL,11,Fpaid employment.
OL,13,FThe team also work with employers to
OL,14,Fdeliver disability training to
OL,15,Fsupported workplaces and help them
OL,16,Funderstand students' needs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
