PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1773256282
OL,3,C'He inspires all of us': Man with
OL,4,Cunique genetic variation gets 'dream
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FNikki Brown, Employer Engagement Lead
OL,8,Fat the charity said: "We've had
OL,9,Fstories from families that are telling
OL,10,Fme about the impact at home, the
OL,11,Fdesire to get up every day and get out
OL,12,Fhas changed.
OL,14,F"You can see with Harry how happy he
OL,15,Fis, he's fulfilled and making friends,
OL,16,Fhe comes home at the end of the day
OL,17,Ftired and happy that he's done a good
OL,18,Fjob."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
